//|     T   -   point:                                               |
//|             * T in [0,1] corresponds to interval spanned by      |
//|               points                                             |
//|             * for non-periodic splines T<0 (or T>1) correspond to|
//|               parts of the curve before the first (after the     |
//|               last) point                                        |
//|             * for periodic splines T<0 (or T>1) are projected    |
